					.card-panel
						.row.box-title
							div.col.s12
								h5.content-headline Full Featured CK Editor
								p CK editor is one of the best editor. It has huge library. It works on JavaScript.
						.row
							.input-field.col.s12
								textarea#editor1(name="editor1", cols="30", rows="10")
							.col.s12
								p
									| Bring rich editor features to your products and websites, providing your users with powerful tools to make creating Web content easier than ever and accessible to anyone.
