									<span class="token function">$</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>document<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">ready</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>
										CKEDITOR<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">replace</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span> <span class="token string">'editor1'</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>
									<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code>
				form.col.s12
					// Inline Editing
					.card-panel
						.row.box-title
							div.col.s12
								h5.content-headline Inline Editing
								p
									| Inline editor provides you the power to update the content in runtime. This is really amazing feature of this editor. You can experience the same for the below example.
						.row
							.col.s12
								div#editor2&attributes({"contenteditable":"true"})
									h5 Envato 
									p Envato Elements is your ultimate subscription for design assets. Get unlimited downloads of templates, actions, fonts, icons & more from top designers for $49/mo. Perfect for agencies, designers & marketers with a regular need for assets. Launching in 2016!
